'''Kel''' is [[Natasha Ross|Chief Ross's]] assistant.

==History==
Kel went over Ross's schedule for the day and noted that it didn't leave time for her to have a lunch break. She told him she just wouldn't have one.

==Career==
He is [[Natasha Ross|Fire Chief Ross's]] assistant.
